snippet.title: Trick Style Trailer 1999
snippet.description:
Trick Style Trailer 1999

Official Content From Acclaim

Go up against the best in the world in an all out, go-for-broke race where the only rule is to win...and win with style. Practice at the velodrome until you have honed your opponent-pounding skills. Feel the speed and trick your way into the new millenium.
Platforms: Sega Dreamcast, PC CD

Sega Dreamcast, PC CD
